Plot: Steve Martin and Bonnie Hunt return as heads of the Baker family who, while on vacation, find themselves in competition with a rival family of eight children, headed by Eugene Levy.
Title: Cheaper by the Dozen 2
Writer: Sam Harper, Craig Titley (characters), Frank B. Gilbreth Jr. (novel), Ernestine Gilbreth Carey (novel)
Actors: Steve Martin, Eugene Levy, Bonnie Hunt, Tom Welling
tomatoConsensus: A sequel to a remake, Cheaper 2 wastes its solid cast in scenes of over-the-top, predictable humor.
